v>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3cb062b elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"3cb062b\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4fd1e56 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"4fd1e56\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9154c3c elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"9154c3c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-image\">\n										<img width=\"1899\" height=\"897\" src=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-1597836058827.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"WooCommerce Store\" srcset=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-1597836058827.png 1899w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-1597836058827-600x283.png 600w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-1597836058827-1600x756.png 1600w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-1597836058827-768x363.png 768w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-1597836058827-1536x726.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1899px) 100vw, 1899px\" title=\"How ReviewX Can Help Any WooCommerce Store To Increase Social Proof & Sales 13\">											</div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ba377f7 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"ba377f7\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-27d4710 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"27d4710\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-db12848 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"db12848\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><h3><b>Step 2: Add Product Criteria For Multi-Criteria Reviews</b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Once the installation is complete, you can use the </span><a href=\"https://reviewx.io/docs/getting-started-with-reviewx-quick-setup/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><b>quick setup wizard of ReviewX</b></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">. The first thing you will need to do is add the appropriate criteria for multi-criteria reviews of your product. This will vary depending on what kind of products you are selling through your WooCommerce store.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">You can also add criteria without using the quick setup wizard by navigating to </span><b>ReviewXSettings Criteria </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">from your WordPress Dashboard and clicking on Add New Criteria as shown below.</span></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6a72a32 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"6a72a32\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3906451 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"3906451\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-812477a elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"812477a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-image\">\n										<img width=\"1600\" height=\"740\" src=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1-1.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Introducing ReviewX: Boost Credibility With Multi-Criteria WooCommerce Reviews & Rating\" srcset=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1-1.png 1600w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1-1-600x278.png 600w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1-1-768x355.png 768w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1-1-1536x710.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" title=\"How ReviewX Can Help Any WooCommerce Store To Increase Social Proof & Sales 14\">											</div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7941767 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"7941767\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-728c2d8 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"728c2d8\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-328f6a7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"328f6a7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">At the moment, you can only add up to three criteria with the free version of ReviewX. However, with <a href=\"https://reviewx.io/#pricing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>ReviewX Pro</strong></a>, you can add an unlimited number of review criteria for your WooCommerce products.</span></p><h3><b>Step 3: Configure Settings To Enable Images, Recommendations And More</b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Once you are done setting up criteria for multi-criteria reviews, you need to configure the settings of ReviewX for WooComemrce.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">To start with, you need to decide when customers should be able to add their reviews. For more information and content rich reviews, you can enable reviews at each stage of the purchasing process. You can do this by navigating to </span><b>wp-admin ReviewX</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> and heading over to the </span><b>Settings</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> tab. </span></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5cd89a3 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"5cd89a3\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-55d6807 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"55d6807\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9bd4032 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"9bd4032\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-image\">\n										<img width=\"1893\" height=\"890\" src=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-1597216026877.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"ReviewX\" srcset=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-1597216026877.png 1893w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-1597216026877-600x282.png 600w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-1597216026877-1600x752.png 1600w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-1597216026877-768x361.png 768w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-1597216026877-1536x722.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1893px) 100vw, 1893px\" title=\"How ReviewX Can Help Any WooCommerce Store To Increase Social Proof & Sales 15\">											</div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-833749e elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"833749e\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-303ccf2 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"303ccf2\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1b66035 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1b66035\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Next, you can toggle the options shown above to allow your customers to share <strong>images and videos</strong> with their reviews. Since reviews with images and videos can make new buyers make a purchase decision more quickly, you can toggle to enable these settings to <strong>increase your WooCommerce sales</strong>. </span></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b0896f3 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"b0896f3\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6023119 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"6023119\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7becd15 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"7becd15\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-image\">\n										<img width=\"1886\" height=\"803\" src=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-1597216512079.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"ReviewX\" srcset=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-1597216512079.png 1886w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-1597216512079-600x255.png 600w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-1597216512079-1600x681.png 1600w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-1597216512079-768x327.png 768w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-1597216512079-1536x654.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1886px) 100vw, 1886px\" title=\"How ReviewX Can Help Any WooCommerce Store To Increase Social Proof & Sales 16\">											</div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ea192fb elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"ea192fb\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-88315eb elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"88315eb\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d96bfb7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d96bfb7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">In addition to this, you can also add options for your customers to recommend your products and share their reviews on social media platforms. It is a great way to gain more credibility and help your WooCommerce store to sell better.</span></p><h3><b>Step 4: Choose A Design Template For Reviews & Ratings Statistics</b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Next, you have to decide how you want to display your product reviews and ratings. With ReviewX, you can get many different attractive design templates to instantly grab your site visitors attention. From graphical representations to choosing the photo review style, template style, and theme color, ReviewX gives you complete freedom to showcase your reviews and rating statistics in such a way that it instantly increases the value of your products to site visitors.</span></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2d63fef elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"2d63fef\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9d3328d elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"9d3328d\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f55b468 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"f55b468\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-image\">\n										<img width=\"1888\" height=\"852\" src=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/axtWlYQY5k.gif\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"How ReviewX Can Help Any WooCommerce Store To Increase Social Proof & Sales 2\" title=\"How ReviewX Can Help Any WooCommerce Store To Increase Social Proof & Sales 17\">											</div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b61c399 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"b61c399\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bfc1eb2 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"bfc1eb2\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c6a4cd9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c6a4cd9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><h3><b>Step 5: Set Up Automatic Email Reminders To Customers</b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Finally, you need to set up automatic email reminders to customers who have made a purchase but have not reviewed your products. You can do this easily by using the automated email reminders feature that comes with Review X. To do this, head over to </span><b>ReviewX Review Email</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">By default, ReviewX comes with an email template complete with all the appropriate placeholders that you may need. These include presets for customers name, shop name, order date, order ID, and much more. You can change the presets and customize the email message as necessary. ReviewX will automatically send the email reminder to your customer.</span></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f547838 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"f547838\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-47cfd8a elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"47cfd8a\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-58727fd elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"58727fd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elemen