v class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b0fb6d0 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"b0fb6d0\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-02d1b1e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"02d1b1e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n			<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">How To Use Elementor To Create Amazing Websites Without Coding</h2>		</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-09747b7 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"09747b7\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-32a9da7 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"32a9da7\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e9e915a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e9e915a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">In this section, were going to give you a step-by-step walkthrough on how to use Elementor to design beautiful websites instantly without coding. Just follow these easy instructions and you are ready to get started with Elementor.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">You need to have your own domain on WordPress to do this. If you don\'t have your own domain and are currently using a site on WordPress.com, then check out our </span><a href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wordpress-com-to-wordpress-org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><b>ultimate guide to move your blog from WordPress.com to WordPress.org</b></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> to start using Elementor.</span></p><h3><b>Step 1: Install & Activate Elementor For WordPress</b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The first step is to install and activate <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/elementor/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>Elementor </strong></a></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">from the WordPress repository by searching for </span><b>Elementor </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">in the search box. Once you have the plugin, just click on </span><b>Install Now</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> and then </span><b>Activate</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> to get started.</span></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-83f7471 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"83f7471\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bb562aa elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"bb562aa\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-59cc20c elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"59cc20c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-image\">\n										<img width=\"1600\" height=\"722\" src=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/INSTALLing-elementor-1-1.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"How To Use Elementor: A Complete Guide For Beginners 3\" srcset=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/INSTALLing-elementor-1-1.png 1600w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/INSTALLing-elementor-1-1-600x271.png 600w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/INSTALLing-elementor-1-1-768x347.png 768w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/INSTALLing-elementor-1-1-1536x693.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" title=\"How To Use Elementor: A Complete Guide For Beginners 29\">											</div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bb7db6b elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"bb7db6b\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ae620c9 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"ae620c9\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5480b48 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5480b48\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><h3><b>Step 2: Create A New Page With Elementor</b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Once you have installed Elementor, you need to navigate to your WordPress dashboard and click on </span><b>Pages Add New</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> to create your websites first landing page. At the very top of your new page you will see a blue button named </span><b>Edit With Elementor</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">. When you click this button, you will be redirected to the</span><b> Elementor Editor</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">.</span></p><p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-503517\" src=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/U8w3V4KNHc-1.gif\" alt=\"How To Use Elementor\" width=\"1600\" height=\"752\" title=\"How To Use Elementor: A Complete Guide For Beginners 30\"></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e76c122 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"e76c122\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1144152 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"1144152\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-74ee490 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"74ee490\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><h3><b>Step 3: Build Your Page With Elementor Editor</b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">If you have successfully completed the above steps, then you should see the </span><b>Elementor Editor</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> on your left hand side. From here you can start designing your page by dragging and dropping any widgets you like anywhere on your page. You can even add new sections to your page to add different elements in different areas of your page.</span></p><p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-502947\" src=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/6cpKHu04A9.gif\" alt=\"How To Use Elementor\" width=\"1600\" height=\"752\" title=\"How To Use Elementor: A Complete Guide For Beginners 31\"></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b8afeda elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"b8afeda\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a80d731 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"a80d731\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7589aec elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"7589aec\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n			<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">How To Use Elementor To Manually Design Your Page Structure</h2>		</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-74c1955 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"74c1955\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d4a9dfa elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"d4a9dfa\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-40865dc elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"40865dc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">With the Elementor Editor, you have the flexibility to customize the entire layout, structure and appearance of your website pages. All you have to do is adjust a few settings in the Elementor Editor and watch the changes in real time.</span></p><h3><b>Step 1: Choose Your Page Layout In Elementor Editor</b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">You can select the layout of your page from the Elementor Editor by clicking on the gear icon and then selecting any of the layout options from the </span><b>Page Layout </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">drop down menu. For this tutorial, we are using the </span><b>Elementor Full Width</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> layout.</span></p><p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-502949\" src=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/ih2poxhssq.gif\" alt=\"How To Use Elementor\" width=\"1600\" height=\"752\" title=\"How To Use Elementor: A Complete Guide For Beginners 32\"></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">You can also choose to toggle the </span><b>Hide Title </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">option from here if you dont want to display your page title. If you want to change the background color of your page, or add a background image to your page, you can click on the </span><b>Style</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> tab and play around with the settings under </span><b>Body Style</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">.</span></p><p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-502950\" src=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/HSu4V17dAr.gif\" alt=\"How To Use Elementor\" width=\"1600\" height=\"752\" title=\"How To Use Elementor: A Complete Guide For Beginners 33\"></p><h3><b>Step 2: Choose Layout Structure For Each Section</b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">By clicking on the </span><b>+ </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">icon above the </span><b>Drag widget here</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> option you can choose the layout structure for each individual section. This is especially useful if you want to add a lot of different elements together in one section, and gives you more flexibility when it comes to designing your web page.</span></p><p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-502954\" src=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/t1Uy9K5y3J.gif\" alt=\"How To Use Elementor\" width=\"1600\" height=\"752\" title=\"How To Use Elementor: A Complete Guide For Beginners 34\"></p><h3><b>Step 3: Add Elements & Move Different Sections</b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Keep adding elements and moving sections until you are happy with the way your page looks. For each element youll see three tabs&#8211;</span><b>Layout, Style </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">and </span><b>Advanced</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">. For every element, the settings under these tabs will be different, so play around with the options until you are satisfied with the appearance of your page.</span></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b8173a3 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"b8173a3\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-32fd733 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"32fd733\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2254cd5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"2254cd5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-image\">\n										<img width=\"1920\" height=\"935\" src=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/chrome_yehkrXcDB7.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"How To Use Elementor: A Complete Guide For Beginners 4\" srcset=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/chrome_yehkrXcDB7.png 1920w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/chrome_yehkrXcDB7-600x292.png 600w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/chrome_