ement and select </span><b>Save As Global</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">. </span></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-df65a8b elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"df65a8b\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-32b0bcc elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"32b0bcc\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-32cdabb elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"32cdabb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-image\">\n										<img width=\"1920\" height=\"874\" src=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/chrome_oLgr3lEqfu.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"How To Use Elementor: A Complete Guide For Beginners 5\" srcset=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/chrome_oLgr3lEqfu.png 1920w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/chrome_oLgr3lEqfu-600x273.png 600w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/chrome_oLgr3lEqfu-1600x728.png 1600w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/chrome_oLgr3lEqfu-768x350.png 768w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/chrome_oLgr3lEqfu-1536x699.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 