figure the settings and customize until you are happy with your Woo checkout page. For further details, </span><strong><a href=\"https://essential-addons.com/elementor/docs/woo-checkout/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">read this documentation</a>.</strong></p><p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-503668\" src=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/EA-Woo-Checkout-10.gif\" alt=\"How To Use Elementor\" width=\"1600\" height=\"726\" title=\"How To Use Elementor: A Complete Guide For Beginners 53\"></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d85fc77 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"d85fc77\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-48f4c10 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"48f4c10\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f3c368c elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f3c368c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n			<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Wrapping Up</h2>		</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2328721 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-se