 Products With Valuable Customer Insight And Feedback</b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">When customers are reviewing your products on the basis of multiple criteria, your business will have a unique opportunity to improve and tailor your products according to their feedback. This can help you satisfy your customers better in the future and thus help you build a loyal customer base in the long run.</span></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0c39aa0 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"0c39aa0\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-af999a9 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"af999a9\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2da8e91 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2da8e91\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n			<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What You Get With ReviewX For WordPress</h2>		</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b6ae166 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"b6ae166\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ada1aa6 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"ada1aa6\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5424929 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5424929\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Now that you know why you need multi-criteria reviews and ratings for your WooCommerce store, lets deep dive into all the amazing features you can get with ReviewX.</span></p><h3><b>Choose Your Own Criteria For Your Product Reviews</b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">With ReviewX you have the flexibility and freedom to choose what criteria to set for your product reviews. For instance, if your </span><b>WooCommerce</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> store focuses on handbags for women, then you can set up multiple review criteria such as material quality, color, design etc. </span></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fc50b15 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"fc50b15\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-73be95a elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"73be95a\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-de7a18a elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"de7a18a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-image\">\n										<img width=\"1600\" height=\"740\" src=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1-1.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Introducing ReviewX: Boost Credibility With Multi-Criteria WooCommerce Reviews & Rating\" srcset=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1-1.png 1600w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1-1-600x278.png 600w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1-1-768x355.png 768w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1-1-1536x710.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" title=\"Introducing ReviewX: Boost Credibility With Multi-Criteria WooCommerce Reviews & Rating 89\">											</div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-589b8cf elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"589b8cf\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-12503f0 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"12503f0\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-116e92b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"116e92b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><h3><b>Easily Sort Customer Reviews & Ratings</b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">In order to influence your site visitors with truly rich, compelling customer content, you have to look through all of your customer reviews to find the most convincing ones. This can be very time consuming if you have to search manually.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">With </span><b>ReviewX</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> however, you can filter customer reviews within seconds. </span><b>ReviewX</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> comes with the option to sort customer reviews and ratings on the basis of recent reviews, photo reviews, text reviews, or top-rated reviews.</span></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-74add86 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"74add86\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f3d0a49 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"f3d0a49\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b5a8766 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"b5a8766\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-image\">\n										<img width=\"1896\" height=\"843\" src=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2-3.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"ReviewX\" srcset=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2-3.png 1896w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2-3-600x267.png 600w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2-3-1600x711.png 1600w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2-3-768x341.png 768w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2-3-1536x683.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1896px) 100vw, 1896px\" title=\"Introducing ReviewX: Boost Credibility With Multi-Criteria WooCommerce Reviews & Rating 90\">											</div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-11ee1c4 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"11ee1c4\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-251fe19 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"251fe19\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bc3e7f1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"bc3e7f1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><h3><b>Advanced Visual Representation To Display Review Statistics</b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">To add further credibility to your WooCommerce store, you might consider displaying the number of good reviews and ratings your products have received in a statistical format. You can do this easily with ReviewX. All you have to do is choose the style of your graph and ReviewX will display all the statistics related to individual products based on the review criteria youve set.</span></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ace85cd elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"ace85cd\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-42c34de elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"42c34de\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-414f0f5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"414f0f5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-image\">\n										<img width=\"1888\" height=\"852\" src=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/axtWlYQY5k.gif\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Introducing ReviewX: Boost Credibility With Multi-Criteria WooCommerce Reviews & Rating 16\" title=\"Introducing ReviewX: Boost Credibility With Multi-Criteria WooCommerce Reviews & Rating 91\">											</div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8644e3c elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"8644e3c\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-33dbb80 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"33dbb80\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d50cb8c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d50cb8c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><h3><b>Boost Credibility & Increase Engagement With Social Sharing</b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">What would be the point of having great reviews and recommendations for your </span><b>WooCommerce</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> store if you couldnt share them on social media? Posting on social media platforms is a great way to engage and interact with potential customers. To help you boost credibility and increase engagement with future customers, </span><b>ReviewX</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> comes with a social share feature so your customers can share what they love about your products and services.</span></p><h3><b>Enable Reviews For Product Order Status</b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The quality of the purchase and delivery process of your online store is just as important as the quality of your products and services. Customers want efficient, easy purchase processes and feedback about their products while they are in transit. They also want to know how good and reliable your refund policies are.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">For this reason, </span><b>ReviewX</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> gives you the option to enable </span><b>Product Order Status</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> reviews so that customers can give instant feedback about every stage of the purchase process. </span></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2e607f1 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"2e607f1\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2865adf elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"2865adf\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a1b4214 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"a1b4214\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-image\">\n										<img width=\"1893\" height=\"890\" src=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-1597216026877.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"ReviewX\" srcset=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-1597216026877.png 1893w, https://wpdev-media.sto