yle=\"font-weight: 400\">In general, reviews with images and videos tend to make richer, more compelling customer content than text-only reviews. Furthermore, reviews with images and videos add more credibility as your site visitors can see what your products look like in real life.</span></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b37cdd5 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"b37cdd5\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6f3e458 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"6f3e458\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d0d5961 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"d0d5961\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-image\">\n										<img width=\"1886\" height=\"803\" src=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-1597216512079.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"ReviewX\" srcset=\"https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-1597216512079.png 1886w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-1597216512079-600x255.png 600w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-1597216512079-1600x681.png 1600w, https://wpdev-media.storage.googleapis.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/screely-